          "relevance": "New objectEnhancements(objectUrl, includeSource) API: given a base PROG/INCL/FUGR, list all enhancement implementations bound to it (with URI, fullname `\\PR:<prog>\\FO:<form>\\SE:<section>\\EI`, mode, replacing flag, optional decoded source, 0-based line/column position) + include expansion that splices enhancement source back into base text. Mirror image of ARC-1's by-name ENHO read. Genuinely useful gap for code-review/impact-analysis workflows. Probe ADT endpoint shape on a4h + BTP first; consider as new SAPRead(type='ENHO', target=...) variant or SAPDiagnose action.",
